data.description: This home is in very prestigious neighborhood in east Fayetteville and has an assumable FHA loan at 5% interest rate.  It's an older home that has been redone recently but has some foundation issues (see attached structural engineer's report and home inspection).  Priced accordingly.  This home is wide open in the living areas and kitchen and features a deck overlooking the backyard, part of which is covered and part of which is screened in.
